#include<stdio.h>
int a[2000];
int main()
{
     int n, i, j, flag;
     for (n = 0; scanf("%d", &a[n]) != EOF; ++n);
    for (i = 0; i < n - 1; ++i)
    {
     flag = 0;
         for (j = 0; j < n - 1 - i; ++j)
            {
                 if (a[j] > a[j + 1])
                  {
                      a[j]=a[j]^a[j+1];
                      a[j+1]=a[j]^a[j+1];
                      a[j]=a[j]^a[j+1];
                      flag = 1;
                   }
            }
    if(flag)
     {
         for (i= 0; i< n; ++i) printf("%d ",a[i]);
         printf("\n");
     }
    }
    return 0;
}
